item.title: Python Coding Grace workshop-August 2016
item.description: Join WITS Ireland at their Python Coding Workshop scheduled for the 23rd August. This workshop is aimed at beginners level. No experience required. The workshop will be lead by Vicky Twomey-Lee from Coding Grace and WITS Ireland. There will be self paced beginners content and resources available to all attendees. Please register at WITS Ireland to secure your place. For more information, please contact Sandra Riordan.
